name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 23
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v23 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Star Fox: Assault, Mario Power Tennis, Virtua Quest, and Metroid Prime 2: Echoes. The disc also features pre-release movie trailers of the following: Star Fox: Assault, Donkey Kong Jungle Beat, NBA Street V3, Dragon Ball Z: Sagas, and the Nintendo DS game system.
